description: This Chainlink VRF top 15% score Parvati purrs with a rating of 65, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 130, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 5 for North, 2 for East, 3 for South, and 3 for West. Parvati has the personality suit of punter. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/40652-52332-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Parvati [130 Votes, Top 15% Score]
